{"tid":115705,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"最強 Linux DDoS 病毒，已出現變種感染 Windows 裝置！","createTime":"2017-02-10T17:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T13:32:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f4c51061597dc7da2b0a0b435406a9b9c1c813","tid":115705,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"原文：<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/28676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F28676&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=6223f938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F28676&h=948824ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/28676</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2017/02/10/170210-28676-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F170210-28676-1.jpg&h=704fda99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／pixabay）<br />\n<br />\n在 2016 年 10 月 21 日癱瘓美國東部網路的 DDoS 攻擊，被發現問題源自於大量物聯網裝置被名為「Mirai」的病毒感染，導致成為殭屍網路、被用於攻擊 DNS 服務商。而現在研究人員發現，Mirai 已經出現變種，可以針對 Windows 系統裝置進行感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n這個狀況由俄羅斯資安服務廠商 Dr.Web 所發現，過去 Mirai 病毒主要用於感染 IoT 物聯網裝置，也就是針對 Linux 系統進行感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。一旦感染後就會將裝置作為殭屍網路一分子，並成為 DDoS 攻擊中大量發送網路需求的單位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2017/02/10/170210-28676-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F170210-28676-2.jpg&h=fec0dd7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／彭博社）<br />\n<br />\n但在 2016 年 10 月 Mirai 原始碼被公開後，Mirai 至今已經變種出可以感染 Windows 裝置的「Trojan.Mirai.1」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。入侵方式是針對 Windows 的密碼進行猜測 ，假使成功入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就藉此繼續感染下一個 Windows 裝置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n「Trojan.Mirai.1」比起 Linux 版本的 Mirai，會監測更多的網路傳輸埠。<span style=\"color: red;\">被感染的 Windows 裝置一旦系統底層是運行 Linux，就會被病毒掌控、成為 DDoS 殭屍網路的一分子。</span>此外若是感染 Microsoft SQL 或 MySQL 資料庫，Mirai還會建立管理者權限、進行更多惡意行為。"},{"pid":"3f1e7546508f40a6ec8aab697fa7f832b7b7234c","tid":115705,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"裝Linux同啲病毒打過囉"},{"pid":"886342259b03e6f5fd2e11db12b0471efcf2d228","tid":115705,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"mr.a講兩句"},{"pid":"6481f29e428f8fa489623d69c4c063db72724da4","tid":115705,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"windows 感染再整衰埋 linux"},{"pid":"1b40eed276111dbd08701470c829d85fb83ede5d","tid":115705,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"然而fresh install既linux機係唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd25efa23d30d06fe4cb6ec617f645b7fa86d96","tid":115705,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"Linux下如何防毒及防hack?"},{"pid":"968e3542f1bfcec509a6132258acac246fc7c40b","tid":115705,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"釣魚"},{"pid":"71c366dd7bbbc71de863fe6a317730a8f5b55429","tid":115705,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"依家出面既清洗公司有無邊間可以防到第七層？"},{"pid":"93a79cf4d54c85af20a627953fe45c092f21bc70","tid":115705,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家出面既清洗公司有無邊間可以防到第七層？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係兩樣野黎<br />\n清洗公司只係filter啲可疑既traffic,比番d正常既traffic 到個客個destination <br />\n<br />\n佢宜家個病毒係令到Linux 底既機都成為疆屍電腦，從而進行ddos <br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ff9ddf8d77c93c083184130886930d36debb30","tid":115705,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家出面既清洗公司有無邊間可以防到第七層？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似係兩樣野黎<br />\n清洗公司只係filter啲可疑既traffic,比番d正常既traffic 到個客個destination <br />\n<br />\n佢宜家個病毒係令到Linux 底既機都成為疆屍電腦，從而進行ddos <br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlinux 個果咁仲仆街喎 ，入左去再ddos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad3b1b3224066219f0effe5b718c765dcdab0db","tid":115705,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Linux下如何防毒及防hack?</blockquote><br />\nmirai係專scan + hack d default password係123456既ip cam之類既iot裝置<br />\n<br />\n冇ssh server/行key only既話，linux server同linux desktop係唔需要防呢d防毒，用少少common sense就夠<br />\n<br />\n防hack睇你開咩service出街，你有個php網頁有sql injection bug既話神仙難救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}